The '''Boffin family''' was a prominent family of [[the Shire]], associated with the region of [[the Yale]] in the [[Eastfarthing]].<ref name="Boffin">{{App|Boffin}}</ref> Important members include [[Berylla Baggins|Berylla Boffin]], who was an ancestor of both [[Bilbo Baggins|Bilbo]] and [[Frodo Baggins]], and [[Folco Boffin]], who helped Frodo in his move from [[Bag End]].<ref>{{FR|I3}}</ref>

